short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple, visual reminder to focus

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Robert Capa captured stunning imagery during the storming of Normandy Beach. Unfortunately, countless rolls of film were lost and never recovered during the war. What remains today are a few precious pieces, none more famous than this one. 

When you open a fresh tab, you're placed in the perspective of the soldier, facing formidable challenges ahead. Across the top, Churchill's quote, a reminder to keep going.
